            <title>[LU-11066] lnet.service doesn&apos;t shutdown before IB causing hang</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11066</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because there are no ib service orderings in lnet.service, systemd may try to stop it after IB shutdown, which hangs IB shutdown.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
